code: public void setPath(String path) {     Assert.notNull(path, "Path must not be null").     Assert.isTrue(path.length() > 1, "Path must have length greater than 1").     Assert.isTrue(path.startsWith("/"), "Path must start with '/'").     this.path = path. }
public Map<String, String> getInit() {     return this.init. }
public void setInit(Map<String, String> init) {     this.init = init. }
